summary: I got the character book yesterday and was wondering which pro would have a chance against Stain, so I looked at their blood...
body:
I got the character book yesterday and was wondering which pro would have a chance against Stain, so I looked at their blood type …

And I noticed something!

Endeavours blood typ is AB!

Shoutos is 0!

If our system of blood types works the same as in thos world, this means it’s IMPOSSIBLE for Endeavour to be his father!

A and B always dominate 0! Even if Shouto got the 0 from his Mum (which he had to anyway or his wouldn’t be 0) his blood typ would be either A (as in A0) or B (as in B0)!


(But it would be possible for a possible brother of Endeavour to be the father, of this man had either 0, A0 or B0… which is possible if their parents had A0 and B0)

(This might just be Horikoshi not thinking of it or something … but… it got me really thinking!)
